Frank Farrington (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Farrington_(actor) 0 Frank Farrington (8 July 1873 in London, England – 27 May 1924 in Los Angeles, California) was an American silent film actor. Frank Farrington choked to death at the height of his acting career in 1924.
